Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最喜欢与最讨厌的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人的推理与悬疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与兰一起去的纽约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.60,0:00:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨和案件都留在回忆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.10,0:00:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和兰以及妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去纽约看歌舞剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.90,0:01:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参观后台时认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演员Heath Flockhart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.60,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heath Flockhart:西斯·弗洛克哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.90,0:01:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人枪杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种东西会夹在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.00,0:02:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一NY事件（解决篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.20,0:02:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能说你们四人从上方射杀他是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.70,0:02:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们现在可以去换衣服了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.10,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 硝烟反应也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样来看 犯人就是外部的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.60,0:02:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 如果不是这样就无法想象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁关的灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时是梳着日本发髻的传统美女演员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时也是惊世侦探小说作家的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隐藏的真实身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是富有灰色脑细胞的女侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Night baroness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.10,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Night baroness:夜晚男爵夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照明师 这边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.60,0:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.90,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷雾散了 警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那盖在舞台和案件上的挡板的迷雾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹牛皮小心吹破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 就照你告诉我的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.10,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.10,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个推理真的准吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.70,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是错了 你妈妈就出丑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.40,0:03:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heath的身高6尺3寸 大约是190厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.40,0:03:47.40,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heath:西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多相当于你的身高加上节目单的长度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.80,0:03:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才量的时候节目单不是从镜子上面露出来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 Heath因为背着翅膀没办法蹲着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是藏在镜子后面头也会露出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 犯人为了让他的头不露出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他用了那个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个可以让演员突然出现在舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或突然消失的舞台特有的装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是镜子后面的地上没有那种出口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有旁边地上有奇怪的铁盖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那里有出口才有盖子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个盖子上夹住了Heath翅膀上掉落的羽毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.60,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖子下面的地面上沾有划成弧状的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.80,0:04:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而舞台上有面包圈状的沟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上沟旁边的帘布松动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能想象到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把面包圈状的舞台旋转起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏起来的地下室就刚好可以打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计找一找的话 会在里面找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被枪击震落的其他羽毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那时溅落的Heath的血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.60,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有手枪射出的子弹壳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有子弹壳就说明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从很近的地方射杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人把铁盖子靠在镜子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上面枪杀了在地下室里等待上场的Heath
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从镜子下面的缝隙和铁盖子的栏杆之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手拿着枪伸过去打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 难道犯人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够做这件事的只有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个场面 晕倒在镜子旁边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rose 只有你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.60,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rose:罗斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rose
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧 这种事不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.40,0:06:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 工作人员没有告诉我们要用地下室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个确实是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说为什么的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是工作人员没有告诉她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大家深信是剧团护身符的镜子破了之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜子很可能就是Rose悄悄弄破的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现那个伤痕的工作人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把镜子破了的部分切下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又合着镜子的高度修改了镜框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏镜子破了的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了不让演员们不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 因为镜子变短了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heath的头就露出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.90,0:06:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果把镜子垫高的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让演员们看出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此使用了本来没有打算用的地下室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Heath的身体隐藏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了Heath和Rose以外 其他演员都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.20,0:07:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么工作人员也告诉Rose了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面包圈状的舞台转动起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.90,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出出口来 使用地下室的事情可以隐瞒过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是罗斯不从镜子下面的缝里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出手盖上地下道的盖子的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就会被拆穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么手枪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个手枪从很高的地方掉下来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺着的姿势能把枪扔上那么高的地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让装扮成天使的Heath把枪吊起来就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 Heath的脖子上有烫伤的痕迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就是Rose把刚用完的枪放在那里弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把枪放在衣服和褶皱上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊到顶突然一停 手枪就会被震落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她没有想到那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Heath沾满血的手抓住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heath手心里的血迹被蹭过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是抓过她手的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 应该还在她手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她右手手套里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满仇恨的Heath的血手印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.80,0:08:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能是把手套翻过来上台的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在开了枪之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急忙把手套翻过来再戴上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使案发之后再调查她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会有硝烟反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.90,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候注意到手套上沾着血的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在化妆间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.30,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见她在打开饮料罐时费了半天劲就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明摘了手套很容易就可以打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有这么做是不是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西藏在手套下面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那时候我也明白了她杀Heath的动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化妆台的镜子上不是贴着的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他两人与Heath十分亲密的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是罗斯贴的却是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.70,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel:天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有Heath扮演的Angel的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱的不是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是他所扮演的Angel
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才让他装扮成Michael去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.90,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael:米迦勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的男人来演那个Michael的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他放弃那个角色是因为说要去演电影啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作决定的是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了Michael的是他自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.90,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明知道我深深爱着他演的Michael
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.30,0:09:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过上帝还是眷顾我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.70,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它救了铠甲掉下来而碰巧衣服被挂在钉子上跑不掉的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sweet angel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 可爱的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me do it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福我才能实现愿望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.50,0:10:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 新一 我必须去警察局做笔录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就叫辆Taxi 先回旅馆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.00,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi:出租车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.80,0:10:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 小心那个杀人魔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日裔男人 好像还是长发的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什么时候都把我当个小孩子看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是高中生了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 Holmes那时是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.20,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes:福尔摩斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是地球绕着月亮转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.90,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一点都不会影响我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.70,0:11:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会还在想刚才Rose和你说的话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说了什么来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.80,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英文我听不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实没说什么重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 关上窗户吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感冒的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.00,0:11:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天早上就说有点发烧不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.50,0:11:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且关上窗户的话就看不清外面纽约的夜景了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.00,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 雨水把座位淋湿了司机很麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 淋湿的地方用手绢擦干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP PLEASE!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.90,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊 是掉在这里的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被风吹走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.00,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是一块手绢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的手绢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Shalon送给我的贵重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.10,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shalon:莎隆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝到底还是不存在的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那个楼梯铁扶手上挂的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是没人住的废弃大楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就拿回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰你先回Taxi里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝要是存在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会有那么悲惨的事发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you,sweet angel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 可爱的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me do it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福我才能实现愿望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道Shalon是知道这些事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rose要杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了杀人犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.50,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那时救了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却让Heath
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.10,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.10,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长 长发的 日本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.20,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up!  Jump in!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点上车啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must be the serial killer!!  Come up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定就是那个杀人魔 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.30,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你是不是日本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.30,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.30,0:13:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有看见一个可疑的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长发 染成银色的卑劣的日本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 谁也没有看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find him, Sir?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到他了吗 长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.60,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I found only a tourist.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.60,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我只找到了一个游客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he hasn't been to this street.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他没有来这条街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The gunfight against us excited the beast…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那野兽刚和我们枪战过 正在兴头上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have gone without catching her
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能放过她这样的猎物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 这里很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个角右转过去就是大街了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里给你叫Taxi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是同伴 我在等同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样高一的男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我跟你和你的同伴只再说一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻给我从这地区消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can we leave her alone?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她一个人留在这好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every crossing to this street is already secured.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条街所有的出口都被封锁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.80,0:14:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个杀人魔在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶紧告诉新一快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西 红色的在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.30,0:15:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是新一的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一出什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.70,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 感冒又发作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 兰 振作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.60,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一不是因为你把手绢吹走了才到这里来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 全是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁下楼来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银 银发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.00,0:16:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.80,0:16:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就是那个杀人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我在这里藏得挺好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那个男孩发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.10,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就恨给你准备了这个下场的上帝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 抓住我的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点 下雨 手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 真是会惹麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.80,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有理由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不想知道人杀人的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.30,0:17:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在人救人的理由里是不会有逻辑性的思考的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊  也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没有注意到这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.80,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你受了伤就表示那些追缉你的人就在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有装消音器就开枪的话他们马上就会闻风而至的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.20,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我现在这个情况也无法抓住你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回就让你走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再遇到你绝不手软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你积累下的罪状和证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆积在阎罗的世界里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.80,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定把你送进监狱 给我好好记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 电视上放了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人魔抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是新一通报的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过警察赶到时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那杀人魔好像已经用枪自杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚发烧睡了一觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息了一晚上 又活蹦乱跳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.90,0:18:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过昨天发生的事情好像都不记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shalon
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你预感到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rose后来要做点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我的第六感一向很准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.40,0:18:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我倒没想到她会杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你能帮我向兰说一声吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也有了Angel
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么好事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.30,0:19:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒还没好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来量一下体温 别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.70,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了没事了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.60,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 就像医生说的已经不烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.70,0:19:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊 好像是过度劳累引起的发烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.30,0:19:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是叫你学习和课外活动都要适可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.50,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你发烧时说了些奇怪的梦话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.20,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么救人 逻辑性思考什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那是只属于我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是只属于我的重要的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不要那么大声说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 明天来接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.50,0:20:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样 全忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从那时开始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.30,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起 我就真的对新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟是怎么了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把这么重要的事都忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是不好的回忆把好的回忆给掩盖住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到那么多人 发生了那么多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.10,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 戴黑色针织帽的那个人是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FBI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.90,0:22:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 发烧休息了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.70,0:22:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪给你手机发的信息也没有回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一也会担心的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.10,0:22:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为“电话”不能用了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.10,0:22:30.00,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注:新一以为全世界的电话都不能用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.30,0:22:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心到哪去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体恢复了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.60,0:22:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.60,0:22:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏感冒还想起了纽约的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个讨厌的案件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.70,0:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 你那个时候很受打击啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.10,0:22:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 好事也想起来很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.70,0:22:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 Shalon的手绢到底怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.40,0:22:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你说给我捡回来的 进入那个废弃大楼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.80,0:23:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个啊 在我这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 放在哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.00,0:23:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天有两件杀人案我想你还是不要想起来的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.30,0:23:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两件 那个杀人魔是自杀的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.70,0:23:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然警察对外公开是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.90,0:23:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场的血还有应该存在的指纹都擦得干干净净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.80,0:23:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要自杀的人你觉得他会这么做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.70,0:23:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能是他要擦掉自己留下的痕迹准备逃跑时被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.50,0:23:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被警察赶到之前来的什么人杀了
